Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.71,0:00:21.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凌辱和服女老板
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.33,0:00:40.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人来的不少\N但你父亲不管预算 购进高档食材
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.48,0:00:44.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.08,0:00:51.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这要在什么时候还给您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.15,0:00:55.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们必须把店变出去吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.69,0:01:05.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说是老店 连带门牌\N卖出去也就1千万
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.57,0:01:09.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只会留下债务而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.11,0:01:15.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过比起继续经营要好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.18,0:01:22.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干脆你就连带店面跟债务\N都拒绝继承好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.25,0:01:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家店是我双亲的心血\N白木家的宝物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.99,0:01:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会继承债务的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.87,0:01:46.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大小姐 请进一步说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.41,0:01:50.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请税等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.29,0:01:59.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.22,0:02:10.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说的对继续经营也是\N入不敷出 还是卖了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.50,0:02:22.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木村你也说这种话\N这店实际上是他的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.64,0:02:34.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子小姐放弃这家店的继承\N您本来就在大公司上班
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.72,0:02:39.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁这个机会回原来单位去吧\N木村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.86,0:02:46.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么时候成了那家伙的人\N难道你忘了我父亲的恩情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.47,0:02:53.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 我只是担心小姐您\N够了 大小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.41,0:03:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样\N下定决心了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.48,0:03:04.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 当然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.15,0:03:10.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我准备好了2份文件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.03,0:03:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是放弃继承权的同意书\N这份是续租的合同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.97,0:03:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要在哪份上签字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.73,0:03:59.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个无法支付现金时\N补加与之相等的代价
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.88,0:04:05.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与之相等的代价\N是指什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.75,0:04:15.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是无法还清时\N由我来决定 有什么不安吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.62,0:04:22.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有 没什么\N这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.63,0:04:27.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就在那份上签字吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.72,0:04:49.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请在旁边盖章\N我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.13,0:05:02.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就可以了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.80,0:05:07.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会将白木交给你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.48,0:05:18.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以了 店是你的 好好还债\N当然会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.04,0:05:42.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.65,0:05:55.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板娘 今天是还债日哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.53,0:06:03.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都过半个月了\N还是这个状态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.13,0:06:12.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也在宣传\N给老顾客打电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.68,0:06:23.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢 有钱吗\N没有 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.69,0:06:35.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 那就按合约上定的\N付出与之相等的代价
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.63,0:06:44.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那与之相等的代价指的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.77,0:07:00.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板娘 好在你是个美女\N要说女人能给男人最好的服务
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.06,0:07:03.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,懂了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.40,0:07:10.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.93,0:07:19.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么能让老板娘做这种事\N你闭嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.34,0:07:30.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就作为利息吧\N能保住家店不是很便宜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.49,0:07:37.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来就是你付不起的金额
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.56,0:07:45.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是这种事 我\N这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.97,0:07:54.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 那算你违约 店是我的\N这样我也比较好做事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.84,0:07:57.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就先告辞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.71,0:08:01.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.65,0:08:08.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再给我点时间吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.39,0:08:17.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天我会带重要客人来\N那时候听你的决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.37,0:08:54.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.97,0:09:06.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中井说的什么意思\N那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.65,0:09:14.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是让你下海的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.46,0:09:18.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然如此啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.67,0:09:34.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我忍过去了\N这家店无论如何都要保住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.54,0:09:39.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是为了逝去的双亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.35,0:09:47.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稻垣先生 请\N谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.84,0:10:07.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家店饭菜不错\N老板娘也漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.24,0:10:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么没客人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.45,0:10:19.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才没钱还债 请您帮忙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.86,0:10:27.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多关照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.06,0:10:38.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只要听我的话 就没什么\N好担心的了 过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.49,0:11:02.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个好女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.32,0:11:25.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这副身体也很不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.39,0:11:31.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我来品尝一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.73,0:11:40.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板娘 可不能这副\N讨厌表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.34,0:11:49.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位可是客人\N是 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.95,0:11:59.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只要乖乖听话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.99,0:12:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体这么紧张\N很敏感啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.26,0:12:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是因为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.60,0:12:49.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很入没做了吧\N老板娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.74,0:12:57.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头抬起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.96,0:13:13.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.36,0:13:16.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.57,0:13:22.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不喜欢吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.64,0:13:28.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.02,0:14:11.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是副好身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.44,0:14:37.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我好好享受番
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.28,0:15:17.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是副好身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.10,0:15:32.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 就这样别动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.91,0:15:41.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好香啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.61,0:16:20.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不错啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.56,0:16:39.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乳头都变硬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.77,0:16:53.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久没被这么摸了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.21,0:17:28.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.69,0:17:36.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里也很久没做了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.23,0:17:40.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢站起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.78,0:18:05.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手放开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.54,0:18:24.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.29,0:18:51.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女人味扑面而来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.95,0:19:50.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈美啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.39,0:20:21.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.06,0:20:36.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是为你好 都是为了你的店\N你懂得吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.60,0:21:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里如何呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.61,0:21:52.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该已经湿润了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.03,0:22:08.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,触感不错啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.73,0:22:43.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腿慢慢张开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.29,0:23:12.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里也有女人味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.72,0:23:47.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面也给我看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.93,0:23:55.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐下张开双腿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.48,0:24:09.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没听到吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:25.23,0:24:29.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板娘\N腿再张开一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:43.52,0:24:45.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在跟我说的一样吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:49.79,0:24:52.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得搞清楚自己的立场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:03.00,0:25:07.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用你美丽的手撑开给我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:14.48,0:25:18.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人都说了\N快做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:49.32,0:25:56.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果真身体美丽的人\N这里也很美啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:00.93,0:26:03.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面也好粉嫩美丽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:26.15,0:26:28.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这里发出的味道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:06.86,0:27:09.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好紧啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:51.44,0:27:53.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:59.31,0:28:03.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是有感觉了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:04.52,0:28:10.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是手指试探了一下\N就这么湿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:32.41,0:28:37.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来让我直接尝尝崃道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:41.36,0:28:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躺下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:08.45,0:29:10.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,味道越来越浓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:52.23,0:29:55.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍不住了\N都发出声音了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:00.37,0:30:02.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越来越湿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:57.62,0:31:00.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要深入了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:10.04,0:31:15.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么弄\N汁液慢慢地出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:07.83,0:32:09.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都湿透了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:51.61,0:32:53.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:05.49,0:33:07.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续摸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:16.70,0:33:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:32.18,0:33:34.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:44.46,0:33:52.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板娘\N快做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:57.40,0:33:59.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是为了店吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:26.90,0:34:28.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用上嘴巴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:55.33,0:35:01.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板娘 这是服务\N得好好做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:07.21,0:35:12.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要含的再深一点\N像这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:20.15,0:35:25.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不行啊\N快继续
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:29.63,0:35:38.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么小的嘴巴 含到喉咙深处\N真受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:47.38,0:35:52.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快一点 含深一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:24.75,0:36:29.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板娘 得让客人开心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:32.49,0:36:37.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 这里套弄起来\N含这里吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:16.67,0:37:19.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续含
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:44.70,0:37:47.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多该结尾了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:50.97,0:37:52.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那躺下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:59.25,0:38:05.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快躺下\N没听到吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:16.33,0:38:19.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躺下来 腿张开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:33.68,0:38:37.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 不要这样\N说什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:43.16,0:38:45.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是已在合约上签约了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:48.90,0:38:53.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然就给我还钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:54.23,0:38:56.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来才更值得期待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:06.04,0:40:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越来越紧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:23.72,0:41:29.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了\N接下来看看你的腰力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:31.59,0:41:32.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:35.86,0:41:38.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板娘\N在干什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:40.40,0:41:41.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:48.68,0:41:51.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跨坐在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:52.28,0:41:53.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己动起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:56.95,0:41:58.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:08.96,0:42:10.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:12.30,0:42:14.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:17.50,0:42:19.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢站起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:44.60,0:42:47.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板娘\N自己动起腰来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:13.83,0:43:18.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板娘 都是为了店啊\N这样动起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:12.69,0:44:14.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:18.56,0:44:24.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,淫荡地摆动腰部\N接下来你自己来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:52.86,0:44:54.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:03.67,0:45:06.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样怎么满足得了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:08.34,0:45:10.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趴下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:11.81,0:45:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屁股翘起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:24.89,0:45:27.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屁股翘高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:07.53,0:47:10.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这真不错\N老板娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:11.67,0:47:19.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再发出好听的声音来\N给我们着看这样漂亮的脸蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:59.31,0:48:01.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:08.92,0:48:10.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腿张开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:25.74,0:48:27.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越来越湿润了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:31.75,0:48:33.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:56.70,0:48:58.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好淫荡的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:10.85,0:49:12.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脸抬起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:11.04,0:50:13.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍不住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:52.42,0:50:58.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板娘 我上的很爽\N还要多关照哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:07.10,0:51:11.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板娘 照这种感觉\N好好赚钱哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:43.14,0:51:44.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:58.89,0:52:05.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在可是开店时间 客人来了\N你这样子可是会被看光的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:06.49,0:52:09.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想被看光吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:14.10,0:52:21.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就乖乖听话\N早点结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:28.65,0:52:33.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来为我的重要客户服务
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:35.46,0:52:40.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为此你得练习怎么服侍男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:43.46,0:52:45.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,练习指的是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:46.80,0:52:51.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不知道男人的愉悦方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:53.34,0:52:58.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么美丽\N没怎么被男人宠爱过吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:00.28,0:53:02.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:07.89,0:53:10.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个年轻小子\N过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:18.03,0:53:19.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:21.37,0:53:25.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板娘\N去含这男人的肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:30.18,0:53:32.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:33.38,0:53:38.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板娘\N怎么能为我做这种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:39.92,0:53:46.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了是练习了\N可不能让我客人扫兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:46.99,0:53:47.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:47.93,0:53:51.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少啰嗦\N尽管做就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:01.14,0:54:02.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:18.63,0:54:19.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:27.57,0:54:28.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:35.44,0:54:37.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不是都立起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:40.91,0:54:44.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板娘\N赶紧做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:47.85,0:54:51.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木村\N对不起啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:10.01,0:55:12.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有用上舌头吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:25.76,0:55:30.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下边也要舔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:45.91,0:55:48.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从下往上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:02.33,0:56:04.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:17.95,0:56:19.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以更深一点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:29.69,0:56:31.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 得这么含
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:49.98,0:56:55.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裤子脱下来一点\N别 别这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:58.39,0:56:59.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:02.12,0:57:05.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板娘 够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:10.26,0:57:14.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板娘 一边含 一边揉蛋蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:44.43,0:57:46.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用左手套弄肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:50.04,0:57:55.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,套弄着\N一边套弄 一遍舔蛋蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:20.47,0:58:22.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两边都不可以停下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:34.21,0:58:37.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样从蛋蛋往上舔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:01.04,0:59:03.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再认真地舔龟头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:19.33,0:59:21.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续含
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:33.74,0:59:38.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续这么做\N就能掌握了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:50.42,0:59:52.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么呢\N别停下
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:12.98,1:00:16.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以一边含\N一边用手套弄
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:18.99,1:00:20.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一边含
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:48.35,1:00:53.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再用力吸\N继续吸
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:09.84,1:01:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再加快速度
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:39.07,1:01:40.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再快一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:21.64,1:02:26.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样\N越来越顺手了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:32.72,1:02:34.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再一会儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:53.94,1:02:55.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再加强刺激
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:44.12,1:03:50.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用忍耐\N可以早点结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:52.13,1:03:53.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:55.47,1:03:59.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板娘\N好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:46.04,1:06:48.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了\N要射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:20.34,1:07:21.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:22.48,1:07:24.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以停下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:33.29,1:07:37.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚就由我手把手教你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:41.96,1:07:46.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也得过来\N我也要吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:36.95,1:08:41.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是迷上老板娘了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:47.36,1:08:51.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就上了\N使劲插
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:56.44,1:08:58.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事怎么可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:01.38,1:09:04.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要不做\N合约就作废
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:08.85,1:09:10.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是为了老板娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:15.52,1:09:17.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样总可以了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:22.06,1:09:23.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木村
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:40.75,1:09:48.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板娘\N这是为了白木\N木村 别这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:56.90,1:09:58.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木村 不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:02.24,1:10:03.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板娘\N对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:12.11,1:10:16.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板娘\N对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:22.79,1:10:24.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板娘\N对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:30.40,1:10:32.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:36.94,1:10:38.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:44.41,1:10:49.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手\N木村
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:57.36,1:10:59.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了\N放开我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:48.74,1:11:53.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板娘\N对不起 这是为了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:54.27,1:12:56.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板娘\N对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:47.39,1:13:54.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快住手\N拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:38.63,1:16:39.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:05.46,1:17:08.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板娘\N对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:39.76,1:17:43.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:01.11,1:18:02.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:05.43,1:21:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板娘\N对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:29.90,1:24:31.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续做
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:35.24,1:24:38.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板娘\N对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:04.00,1:26:11.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板娘 这是为了保住店\N原谅我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:51.51,1:26:57.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板娘\N对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:43.49,1:28:46.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了\N这么快就要射了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:49.63,1:28:54.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就射老板娘脸上
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:57.24,1:29:00.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是为了你们的店\N射吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:10.58,1:29:12.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原谅我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:40.01,1:30:41.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:12.57,1:31:13.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起\N老板娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:14.71,1:31:19.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是挺好的吗\N能跟最爱的老板娘做
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:23.52,1:31:24.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚开
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:30.46,1:31:33.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也来一次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:41.40,1:31:43.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:46.74,1:31:54.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎样 这边声音不错哦\N都湿透了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:02.62,1:32:03.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:08.63,1:32:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么湿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:42.40,1:32:43.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是诚实一点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:53.21,1:32:55.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她也不过是个女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:03.35,1:33:05.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实很舒服吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:34.45,1:33:36.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:50.73,1:33:52.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么不要啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:56.34,1:33:58.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都到这份上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:03.41,1:34:05.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实强势一点更好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:09.95,1:34:11.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女人不就是这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:28.37,1:34:34.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快承认吧\N诚实一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:36.64,1:34:37.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样比较轻松
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:03.07,1:35:04.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又要进去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:30.70,1:35:31.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:36.44,1:35:38.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板娘\N要看的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:42.04,1:35:43.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,张开眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:53.25,1:35:54.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:57.79,1:35:59.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我看着
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:43.84,1:36:45.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好体会
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:04.79,1:37:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:20.41,1:37:22.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么舒服吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:51.51,1:37:58.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给构好看看\N看下面
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:12.86,1:38:14.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有在看吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:52.90,1:38:55.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要继续插的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:24.80,1:39:26.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:34.41,1:39:38.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒插到小穴里很舒服吧\N老板娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:46.42,1:39:48.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是很想要
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:17.52,1:40:20.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是挺好的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:28.33,1:40:30.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小穴很不错哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:45.68,1:40:46.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:54.62,1:40:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:30.66,1:41:33.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想停吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:44.40,1:41:45.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:48.01,1:41:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睁开眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:01.62,1:42:04.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小穴很不错哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:06.69,1:42:07.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真让人受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:21.17,1:43:22.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:26.64,1:43:28.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:31.98,1:43:35.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要辞职
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:45.33,1:43:47.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是你的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:53.73,1:43:56.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算可以呈现给客人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:13.22,1:44:15.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来喝一杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:20.96,1:44:27.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板娘很快就来 您边吃边等\N好期待啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:30.44,1:44:32.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失礼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:35.11,1:44:36.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:44.05,1:44:49.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人您好 欢迎光临\N我是老板娘 白木优子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:50.86,1:44:55.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真心实意为您服务
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:00.47,1:45:07.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺美的啊\N失礼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:21.96,1:45:23.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失礼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:33.83,1:45:38.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外套给我\N麻烦您了
